  "description": "The manuscript titled \"Genetic Dissection of Protein Content in\n Cowpea Using Custom-made NIRS equations and GWAS as a Model for\n Nutritional Breeding and Undergraduate Research Training\" examines\n the genetic basis of grain protein content in cowpea (black-eye pea), a\n key crop for food and nutrition security. The authors evaluated 287\n diverse cowpea accessions using a species-specific near-infrared\n spectroscopy model with high accuracy to estimate protein levels.",
